    • getCommandMessageName

      public static String getCommandMessageName(int cmd)
      Converts a command value to a user-friendly name
      Parameters:
      cmd - The command value
      Returns:
      The user-friendly name - if not one of the defined SSH_FXP_XXX values then returns the string representation of the command's value

    • getStatusName

      public static String getStatusName(int status)
      Converts a return status value to a user-friendly name
      Parameters:
      status - The status value
      Returns:
      The user-friendly name - if not one of the defined SSH_FX_XXX values then returns the string representation of the status value
